room_title: Escape room "Queen Anne's Revenge" by Victor Valley Escape in Hesperia
room_description:
You and half of your crew have snuck on board the evil Captain Blackbeard’s ship to steal his prized medallion, which is rumored to give him immortality. You all get caught by Blackbeard and locked away. He says he will be back in 60 minutes to make you walk the plank.
Luckily for you, your shipmates have snuck on board to rescue you. You must work together to secure your freedom, find Blackbeard’s medallion and get back to your ship.
